      "title": "Code from custom node",
      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": [
        "## Code: ModelSampling Proxy\n\n### Custom Node (`nodes/nodes_z_image_turbo.py`)\n\n```python\nclass ModelSamplingAuraFlow_ZIMG(io.ComfyNode):\n    @classmethod\n    def execute(cls, model, shift):\n        m = model.clone()\n        # model.clone() triggers RPC to host\n        # host clones real ModelPatcher\n        # child gets new proxy reference\n\n        class ModelSamplingAdvanced(\n            sampling_base, sampling_type\n        ):\n            pass\n\n        model_sampling = ModelSamplingAdvanced(\n            model.model.model_config\n        )\n        model_sampling.set_parameters(\n            shift=shift, multiplier=1.0\n        )\n        m.add_object_patch(\n            'model_sampling', model_sampling\n        )\n        return io.NodeOutput(m)\n```\n\n### Proxy Files\n\n`comfy/isolation/model_patcher_proxy.py`:\n- `ModelPatcherProxy` — clone, patch, apply, unpatch\n- VRAM headroom pre-allocation\n- `_InnerModelProxy` for `.model` access\n\n`comfy/isolation/model_patcher_proxy_registry.py`:\n- `ModelPatcherRegistry` — host-side operations\n- Lease-based synchronization\n- State snapshots for RPC\n\n`comfy/isolation/model_sampling_proxy.py`:\n- `ModelSamplingProxy` / `ModelSamplingRegistry`\n- sigma calculations forwarded via RPC\n"
      ],
      "color": "#432",
      "bgcolor": "#000"
    },
